features: [LIGHTWEIGHT AND EASY INSTALLATION] The DIY computer case is made of aluminum alloy material, which makes it lightweight and easy to install and disassemble. It can be stacked on top of each other, saving space.

[GOOD HEAT DISSIPATION] With its open frame design, this computer case provides excellent heat dissipation, making it suitable for overclocking testing. It ensures stable and efficient performance for your PC.

[ENJOY THE FUN OF DIY] This computer case features a simple structure that allows for easy assembling. You can fully enjoy the fun of DIY and customize your PC according to your needs and preferences.
[PRECISE HOLE POSITION] The computer case adopts high-specification craft with precise hole position, making it convenient for installation. It ensures a secure and stable fit for your components.
[STURDY AND DURABLE] Made of excellent 20x20 aluminum alloy material, this computer case is sturdy and durable. It also supports ATX ordinary large power supply, providing reliable power for your PC.
